&lt;li&gt;Perform accurate 3D camera and object tracking in live-action plates with or without on-set measurements and lidar scans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement best practices in our tracking pipeline, ensuring the environment and object tracking are seamlessly matched to the camera and puppet facial performances.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hand-key and solve complex motion where automated solutions fall short.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver clean and tight matchmove data, including STMaps, to layout, animation, and compositing departments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create rotomation of CG character rigs to match puppet movement, as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain output quality and momentum in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the VFX and CG teams to troubleshoot tracking challenges and maintain alignment with production needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
